  <TR><TD BGCOLOR="#fff5ba" WIDTH="150"><B>Procedural History</B></TD></TR>
  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">This is an action to recover Federal<BR ALIGN='left'/>income taxes paid by petitioner for the<BR ALIGN='left'/>fiscal year ended June 30, 1960. The<BR ALIGN='left'/>issues involve the proper<BR ALIGN='left'/>characterization for tax purposes of the<BR ALIGN='left'/>transaction in question, and the tax<BR ALIGN='left'/>treatment of the resulting gain.</TD></TR>
